OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy, with early patchy light
OL,6,Frain or drizzle possible. Then
OL,7,Fbecoming dry and brighter for most
OL,8,Fplaces with some sunny intervals
OL,9,Fgradually developing, but also perhaps
OL,10,Fisolated light coastal showers. Light
OL,11,Fnortherly winds inland, breezy and
OL,12,Fcooler along the coast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FClear spells and patchy
OL,15,Fcloud, with a chance of isolated light
OL,16,Fshowers reaching coastal areas, where
OL,17,Fit will become windy. Becoming cooler
OL,18,Ffor many places, compared to recent
OL,19,Fnights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
